      <title>货币/资金的时间价值(Time value of money)</title>
      <link href="/2018/08/31/Time-value-of-money/"/>
      <url>/2018/08/31/Time-value-of-money/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<hr><h1 id="收益率的常见英文表述：Return-yield-或-interest-rate"><a href="#收益率的常见英文表述：Return-yield-或-interest-rate" class="headerlink" title="收益率的常见英文表述：Return, yield 或 interest rate"></a>收益率的常见英文表述：Return, yield 或 interest rate</h1><a id="more"></a><p>三者的含义完全相同</p><blockquote><p>注： 习惯上，股票常用return</p></blockquote><h2 id="其他收益率的区分"><a href="#其他收益率的区分" class="headerlink" title="其他收益率的区分:"></a>其他收益率的区分:</h2><h4 id="Interest-rate-of-return-要求回报率"><a href="#Interest-rate-of-return-要求回报率" class="headerlink" title="Interest rate of return 要求回报率"></a>Interest rate of return 要求回报率</h4><p>affected by the supply and demand of funds in the market</p><h4 id="Discounted-rate-折现率"><a href="#Discounted-rate-折现率" class="headerlink" title="Discounted rate 折现率"></a>Discounted rate 折现率</h4><p>与interest rate可互换使用</p><h4 id="Opportunity-cost-机会成本"><a href="#Opportunity-cost-机会成本" class="headerlink" title="Opportunity cost 机会成本"></a>Opportunity cost 机会成本</h4><p>指次优方案下丧失的收益</p><h1 id="Required-rate-of-return的分解"><a href="#Required-rate-of-return的分解" class="headerlink" title="Required rate of return的分解"></a>Required rate of return的分解</h1><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Required interest rate of return on a security </span><br><span class="line">= nominal risk-free rate （名义（包含通胀）无风险收益率，</span><br><span class="line">即买美国国债的收益率，其他国家有sovereign risk主权风险）</span><br><span class="line">+ default risk premium （违约风险溢价）</span><br><span class="line">+ liquidity risk premium （流动性风险溢价）</span><br><span class="line">+ maturity risk premium （到期日风险溢价）</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Nominal risk-free rate </span><br><span class="line">= real risk-free rate </span><br><span class="line">+ expected inflation rate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="EAR-（effective-annualized-return）有效年化利率"><a href="#EAR-（effective-annualized-return）有效年化利率" class="headerlink" title="EAR （effective annualized return）有效年化利率"></a>EAR （effective annualized return）有效年化利率</h1><p>Nominal rate：名义年利率 r<br>复利频率为 N<br>EAR=(1+r/N)^N-1 → e^r-1（continuous componding 连续复利）</p><p>结论：复利频率N越大，EAR越大，与stated rate之间差异越大</p><blockquote><p>注：<br>美国存款和贷款都是复利的；<br>持有T年 HPY=e^（rT）-1</p></blockquote><h1 id="Annuity-年金"><a href="#Annuity-年金" class="headerlink" title="Annuity 年金"></a>Annuity 年金</h1><h4 id="计算注意点：N是期数，I-Y是每一期的利率，C-R-work，流入为正流出为负"><a href="#计算注意点：N是期数，I-Y是每一期的利率，C-R-work，流入为正流出为负" class="headerlink" title="计算注意点：N是期数，I/Y是每一期的利率，C/R work，流入为正流出为负"></a>计算注意点：N是期数，I/Y是每一期的利率，C/R work，流入为正流出为负</h4><h4 id="AMORT：使用计算器"><a href="#AMORT：使用计算器" class="headerlink" title="AMORT：使用计算器"></a>AMORT：使用计算器</h4><p>P1      从哪期开始<br>P2      到哪期结束<br>BAL      尚未还本金<br>PRN     本金还款<br>INT     还的利息</p><h4 id="三种年金的区分"><a href="#三种年金的区分" class="headerlink" title="三种年金的区分"></a>三种年金的区分</h4><p>ordinary annuities 普通年金，后付年金<br>annuity due 先付年金 等于后付年金*（1+r）<br>perpetuity 永续年金 PV=A/r</p><h1 id="其他"><a href="#其他" class="headerlink" title="其他"></a>其他</h1><p>rounding error 舍入误差<br>outstanding balance 末期余额</p>]]></content>
      
